            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pork has caramelised, add the <strong>spinach</strong> to the pan with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> boiled water</strong> and cook, covered for 2 min until the spinach has started to wilt</p><p>Meanwhile, slice the <strong>spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> finely</p><p>Crush the <strong>peanuts</strong> in their bag with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
